review: Dr Geeta Karla is an exceptional dentist. She has a steady hand and her staff is welcoming. She explained the procedure and tangible cost associated to each. Thus, assuring me that I am getting a correct procedure along with an awesome value. She did a thorough job of providing cleaning and requested me for a follow up visit. I was surprised to see that dentistry has improved so much in India from the heydays as all the latest tools and knowledge is being utilized here. It is a recommendation that all the people who chew tobacco related products and/or consume a diet rich with sugar and/or acidity regularly visit a doctor and a dentist. As they say, Prevention is better than a cure.
